title: The reason why some photos / video files cannot be opened
answer:
1. The file format is not supported by the phone 

 2. The memory space of the phone is insufficient 

 3. The file is corrupted 

 4. The file is copy protected (files with the format of dcf) 

 5. If the phone resource is low, please close some opened third-party applications to consume the phoneâ€™s resources 

 6. In rare cases where the mobile application or system has unknown errors, try restarting the phone
